+┊  ┊29┊    createdAt: Date! # when message was created
 ┊ 4┊30┊  }
-┊ 5┊  ┊  schema {
-┊ 6┊  ┊    query: Query
-┊ 7┊  ┊  }`,
-┊ 8┊  ┊];
+┊  ┊31┊`];
 ┊ 9┊32┊
